{"tid":2460433,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–痴肥導致糖尿病的其中一道論述","createTime":"2021-03-24T23:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T22:14:07.000Z","uid":38861,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fca375e42a0a730dca1ecc97b58dae49277e14e0","tid":2460433,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:50:33.000Z","msg":"痴肥一直被譽為會增加患上糖尿病的機會。而箇中的理論，現今仍有著爭議的空間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTFSCkxMn4ubriG7Tx4EVBG3MtgDEe8h2u2CWALn7Q9pp?filename=A7TfWq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7TfWq8.jpg&h=9e26764f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本集將會討論眾多理論之中的其中一種，adipose tissue expandability hypothesis。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）Adipose tissue expandability hypothesis的理論就是，身體專責儲存脂肪的脂肪細胞不勝負荷，無法再繼續膨脹增大儲存脂肪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPTScvpN4yStRiyCegSy9kR7ThD7Z5jswPX5YAasvQfrM?filename=4jTjDEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jTjDEv.jpg&h=37051545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正因如此，身體其他的細胞例如心臟細胞、肌肉細胞、胰臟細胞等亦唯有幫忙儲存脂肪。<br />\n<br />\n而這樣做的後果不但會損毀各種細胞的運作及功能，亦大大減低它們對胰島素的反應，導致血糖長期高企(糖尿病)。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）同時間，歲數增長亦是增加患上糖尿病的風險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUJYLYVeyGMNA8NAwrsipu7FvjhF2syGV6igxxuep9VG8?filename=RckesxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRckesxU.jpg&h=13625df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，處於45-65歲的癡肥患者，其真正專責儲存脂肪的脂肪細胞存量是比同齡健康人士少25%左右。<br />\n<br />\n而天生因基因變異(PPARy, Sepin/ BCSL2, Lamin A和AKT2)而患上全身脂肪失養症的患者，脂肪細胞比例比正常人為少，其身體細胞出奇的更容易對胰島素不產生反應，導致更容易患上糖尿病。<br />\n<br />\n這兩點亦是Adipose tissue expandability hypothesis的重要支持理據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=df6427f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=9b60668a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0308814620325899?via%3Dihub#t0010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0308814620325899%3Fvia%253Dihub%23t0010&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e8645874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0308814620325899?via%3Dihub#t0010</a>"},{"pid":"6b095c3a68b59657a1dd55cb22665b7461337edf","tid":2460433,"uid":30113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:51:34.000Z","msg":"like"},{"pid":"a56f001b9bff68642f0593d4ee01205c9c979f8e","tid":2460433,"uid":117318,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:54:14.000Z","msg":"薯巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa